<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>13×13 – Coming Soon</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;background:#2D3640;color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;text-align:center}
h1{font-size:3.5rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
.accent{color:#B8293D}
.sub{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:3rem}
.soon{font-size:0.95rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);padding-top:2rem;margin-top:2rem}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div>
<h1>13<span class="accent">×</span>13</h1>
<p class="sub">Walliser Perspektiven</p>
<p class="soon">Bald verfügbar.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
